46:26.720 --> 46:28.920
♪ You turn me on

46:31.280 --> 46:33.240
♪ You lift me up

46:33.240 --> 46:38.400
♪ Like the sweetest cup,
I'd share with you

46:40.200 --> 46:43.360
♪ You lift me up

46:43.360 --> 46:45.440
♪ Don't you ever stop

46:45.440 --> 46:48.400
♪ I'm here with you

46:49.840 --> 46:52.720
♪ Now it's all or nothing

46:52.720 --> 46:57.760
♪ 'Cause you said
you'll follow through ♪

47:03.560 --> 47:05.200
Sweet, mate?

47:06.480 --> 47:08.080
Yeah.

47:08.080 --> 47:09.840
Sweet.

47:16.520 --> 47:18.000
Here.

47:19.520 --> 47:21.200
You're cold.

47:30.320 --> 47:36.320
♪ BLACK LACE: Do the Conga ♪

47:40.840 --> 47:44.480
♪ Do-do-dooo,
come on and the conga. ♪

47:50.120 --> 47:54.520
Listen, I know you might be
ashamed of our past,

47:54.520 --> 47:56.280
but I'm not.

47:56.280 --> 47:59.320
You think I'm ashamed?
You couldn't wait to get shot of me.

47:59.320 --> 48:01.880
That's because
it's not safe for you here.

48:01.880 --> 48:03.560
Is it that,

48:03.560 --> 48:07.120
or is it that you just don't want me
to be part of your new family?

48:08.800 --> 48:10.600
They're not my family.

48:16.080 --> 48:17.760
They're nothing to me.

48:17.760 --> 48:20.640
So, why the fuck are you still here?

48:24.120 --> 48:27.240
To kill every last one of them.

